    "markdown": "---\ntitle: Miscellaneous Projects\ndescription: A collection of miscellaneous projects that may or may not be related to my research.\npreview: images/lab/john_helveston_circle.png\nexecute: \n  echo: false\n  message: false\n  warning: false\nformat:\n  html: \n    css: css/strapless.css\n---\n\n\n::: {.cell}\n::: {.cell-output-display}\n\n```{=html}\n<div>\n<div class=\"row p-0 row-cols-1 row-cols-md-2 row-cols-lg-3\" style=\"margin-left: -.2rem; margin-right: -.2rem; margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; \">\n<div class=\"card bg-transparent m-0 border-0 collapse.show bs4cards-blahblahblah \" style=\"padding: .2rem ; border-width: 0; border-radius: 1rem 1rem 1rem 1rem ;\">\n<a href=\"https://jhelvy.github.io/logitr/\" style=\"color: inherit;\">\n<img src=\"images/hex/logitr.png\" class=\"card-img-top\" style=\"border-style:solid; border-color:inherits; border-width:1px 1px 0 1px; border-radius: 1rem 1rem 0 0 ;\"/>\n</a>\n<div class=\"card-body justify-content-end m-0 p-0\" style=\"visibility: visible; background-color: #FFFFFFFF; border-style:solid; border-color:inherits; border-width:1px; border-radius: 0 0 1rem 1rem ;\">\n<a href=\"https://jhelvy.github.io/logitr/\">\n<h5 class=\"card-title my-auto px-3 pt-3 pb-1\">logitr</h5>\n</a>\n<p class=\"card-text my-auto px-3 pb-3 pt-1\">R package for fast estimation of multinomial and mixed logit models with preference space and willingness to pay space utility parameterizations.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"card bg-transparent m-0 border-0 collapse.show bs4cards-blahblahblah \" style=\"padding: .2rem ; border-width: 0; border-radius: 1rem 1rem 1rem 1rem ;\">\n<a href=\"https://jhelvy.github.io/cbcTools/\" style=\"color: inherit;\">\n<img src=\"images/hex/cbcTools.png\" class=\"card-img-top\" style=\"border-style:solid; border-color:inherits; border-width:1px 1px 0 1px; border-radius: 1rem 1rem 0 0 ;\"/>\n</a>\n<div class=\"card-body justify-content-end m-0 p-0\" style=\"visibility: visible; background-color: #FFFFFFFF; border-style:solid; border-color:inherits; border-width:1px; border-radius: 0 0 1rem 1rem ;\">\n<a href=\"https://jhelvy.github.io/cbcTools/\">\n<h5 class=\"card-title my-auto px-3 pt-3 pb-1\">cbcTools</h5>\n</a>\n<p class=\"card-text my-auto px-3 pb-3 pt-1\">R package with tools for designing choice based conjoint (cbc) survey experiments and conducting power analyses.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"card bg-transparent m-0 border-0 collapse.show bs4cards-blahblahblah \" style=\"padding: .2rem ; border-width: 0; border-radius: 1rem 1rem 1rem 1rem ;\">\n<a href=\"https://surveydown.org/\" style=\"color: inherit;\">\n<img src=\"images/hex/surveydown.png\" class=\"card-img-top\" style=\"border-style:solid; border-color:inherits; border-width:1px 1px 0 1px; border-radius: 1rem 1rem 0 0 ;\"/>\n</a>\n<div class=\"card-body justify-content-end m-0 p-0\" style=\"visibility: visible; background-color: #FFFFFFFF; border-style:solid; border-color:inherits; border-width:1px; border-radius: 0 0 1rem 1rem ;\">\n<a href=\"https://surveydown.org/\">\n<h5 class=\"card-title my-auto px-3 pt-3 pb-1\">surveydown</h5>\n</a>\n<p class=\"card-text my-auto px-3 pb-3 pt-1\">R package for generating markdown-based surveys using Quarto shiny documents.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"card bg-transparent m-0 border-0 collapse.show bs4cards-blahblahblah \" style=\"padding: .2rem ; border-width: 0; border-radius: 1rem 1rem 1rem 1rem ;\">\n<a href=\"https://github.com/jhelvy/wireless-corne/\" style=\"color: inherit;\">\n<img src=\"images/wireless_corne.jpeg\" class=\"card-img-top\" style=\"border-style:solid; border-color:inherits; border-width:1px 1px 0 1px; border-radius: 1rem 1rem 0 0 ;\"/>\n</a>\n<div class=\"card-body justify-content-end m-0 p-0\" style=\"visibility: visible; background-color: #FFFFFFFF; border-style:solid; border-color:inherits; border-width:1px; border-radius: 0 0 1rem 1rem ;\">\n<a href=\"https://github.com/jhelvy/wireless-corne/\">\n<h5 class=\"card-title my-auto px-3 pt-3 pb-1\">Wireless Corne</h5>\n</a>\n<p class=\"card-text my-auto px-3 pb-3 pt-1\">Build log and gallery of how I built my wireless Corne keyboard.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"card bg-transparent m-0 border-0 collapse.show bs4cards-blahblahblah \" style=\"padding: .2rem ; border-width: 0; border-radius: 1rem 1rem 1rem 1rem ;\">\n<a href=\"https://distillery.rbind.io/\" style=\"color: inherit;\">\n<img src=\"images/hex/distillery.png\" class=\"card-img-top\" style=\"border-style:solid; border-color:inherits; border-width:1px 1px 0 1px; border-radius: 1rem 1rem 0 0 ;\"/>\n</a>\n<div class=\"card-body justify-content-end m-0 p-0\" style=\"visibility: visible; background-color: #FFFFFFFF; border-style:solid; border-color:inherits; border-width:1px; border-radius: 0 0 1rem 1rem ;\">\n<a href=\"https://distillery.rbind.io/\">\n<h5 class=\"card-title my-auto px-3 pt-3 pb-1\">The Distillery</h5>\n</a>\n<p class=\"card-text my-auto px-3 pb-3 pt-1\">Distill website showcasing other distill websites and blogs.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"card bg-transparent m-0 border-0 collapse.show bs4cards-blahblahblah \" style=\"padding: .2rem ; border-width: 0; border-radius: 1rem 1rem 1rem 1rem ;\">\n<a href=\"https://jhelvy.github.io/oica/\" style=\"color: inherit;\">\n<img src=\"images/hex/oica.png\" class=\"card-img-top\" style=\"border-style:solid; border-color:inherits; border-width:1px 1px 0 1px; border-radius: 1rem 1rem 0 0 ;\"/>\n</a>\n<div class=\"card-body justify-content-end m-0 p-0\" style=\"visibility: visible; background-color: #FFFFFFFF; border-style:solid; border-color:inherits; border-width:1px; border-radius: 0 0 1rem 1rem ;\">\n<a href=\"https://jhelvy.github.io/oica/\">\n<h5 class=\"card-title my-auto px-3 pt-3 pb-1\">oica</h5>\n</a>\n<p class=\"card-text my-auto px-3 pb-3 pt-1\">R data package with tidy formatted data on vehicle production and sales from the International Organization of Motor Vehicle Manufacturers.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"card bg-transparent m-0 border-0 collapse.show bs4cards-blahblahblah \" style=\"padding: .2rem ; border-width: 0; border-radius: 1rem 1rem 1rem 1rem ;\">\n<a href=\"https://jhelvy.github.io/magaScreener/\" style=\"color: inherit;\">\n<img src=\"images/magaScreener.png\" class=\"card-img-top\" style=\"border-style:solid; border-color:inherits; border-width:1px 1px 0 1px; border-radius: 1rem 1rem 0 0 ;\"/>\n</a>\n<div class=\"card-body justify-content-end m-0 p-0\" style=\"visibility: visible; background-color: #FFFFFFFF; border-style:solid; border-color:inherits; border-width:1px; border-radius: 0 0 1rem 1rem ;\">\n<a href=\"https://jhelvy.github.io/magaScreener/\">\n<h5 class=\"card-title my-auto px-3 pt-3 pb-1\">magaScreener</h5>\n</a>\n<p class=\"card-text my-auto px-3 pb-3 pt-1\">Tool for analyzing documents for specific MAGA-targeted keywords, intended to be used to help identify words that might get screened by the federal government.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"card bg-transparent m-0 border-0 collapse.show bs4cards-blahblahblah \" style=\"padding: .2rem ; border-width: 0; border-radius: 1rem 1rem 1rem 1rem ;\">\n<a href=\"https://jhelvy.github.io/renderthis/\" style=\"color: inherit;\">\n<img src=\"images/hex/renderthis.png\" class=\"card-img-top\" style=\"border-style:solid; border-color:inherits; border-width:1px 1px 0 1px; border-radius: 1rem 1rem 0 0 ;\"/>\n</a>\n<div class=\"card-body justify-content-end m-0 p-0\" style=\"visibility: visible; background-color: #FFFFFFFF; border-style:solid; border-color:inherits; border-width:1px; border-radius: 0 0 1rem 1rem ;\">\n<a href=\"https://jhelvy.github.io/renderthis/\">\n<h5 class=\"card-title my-auto px-3 pt-3 pb-1\">renderthis</h5>\n</a>\n<p class=\"card-text my-auto px-3 pb-3 pt-1\">R package for rendering slides and other media into different formats, including html, pdf, png, gif, pptx, and mp4.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"card bg-transparent m-0 border-0 collapse.sho