le=\"color: inherit;\">\n<img src=\"images/splitKbCompare.png\" class=\"card-img-top\" style=\"border-style:solid; border-color:inherits; border-width:1px 1px 0 1px; border-radius: 1rem 1rem 0 0 ;\"/>\n</a>\n<div class=\"card-body justify-content-end m-0 p-0\" style=\"visibility: visible; background-color: #FFFFFFFF; border-style:solid; border-color:inherits; border-width:1px; border-radius: 0 0 1rem 1rem ;\">\n<a href=\"https://jhelvy.shinyapps.io/splitKbCompare/\">\n<h5 class=\"card-title my-auto px-3 pt-3 pb-1\">splitKbCompare</h5>\n</a>\n<p class=\"card-text my-auto px-3 pb-3 pt-1\">Interactive R Shiny app for comparing layouts of different split mechanical keyboards. Built for the ergonomic keyboard community r/ErgoMechKeyboards.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"card bg-transparent m-0 border-0 collapse.show bs4cards-blahblahblah \" style=\"padding: .2rem ; border-width: 0; border-radius: 1rem 1rem 1rem 1rem ;\">\n<a href=\"https://jhelvy.github.io/lexis/\" style=\"color: inherit;\">\n<img src=\"images/lexis.png\" class=\"card-img-top\" style=\"border-style:solid; border-color:inherits; border-width:1px 1px 0 1px; border-radius: 1rem 1rem 0 0 ;\"/>\n</a>\n<div class=\"card-body justify-content-end m-0 p-0\" style=\"visibility: visible; background-color: #FFFFFFFF; border-style:solid; border-color:inherits; border-width:1px; border-radius: 0 0 1rem 1rem ;\">\n<a href=\"https://jhelvy.github.io/lexis/\">\n<h5 class=\"card-title my-auto px-3 pt-3 pb-1\">λέξις (lexis)</h5>\n</a>\n<p class=\"card-text my-auto px-3 pb-3 pt-1\">Theme for xaringan slides with a light gray background, \"Fira Sans Condensed\" for headers, “Roboto” for body text.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"card bg-transparent m-0 border-0 collapse.show bs4cards-blahblahblah \" style=\"padding: .2rem ; border-width: 0; border-radius: 1rem 1rem 1rem 1rem ;\">\n<a href=\"https://p4a.jhelvy.com\" style=\"color: inherit;\">\n<img src=\"images/hex/p4a.png\" class=\"card-img-top\" style=\"border-style:so